/* planning -- isn't it symbolic, aka automaton? */
/* be aware that understanding is not knowing how to */
/* understanding means I heard about it; planing is how to do it; for example: I understand what you want to accomplish, but I have no idea how to do it */
/* know how is understating and having a cached plan/algorithm -- know how is a cached plan/algorithm, aka script or plan; so: we need intelligence to create new plan/algorithm */
